snippet.title: Fitness Boxing - Overview Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Get moving with fun, boxing-based rhythmic exercises set to the instrumental beats of songs by popular artists. You can personalize your workouts by selecting from different fitness goals. Train your way, whether you’re on your own, with a friend, at home, or on the go! Now you can work out anytime, anywhere on the Nintendo Switch system! Start establishing a routine by downloading the free, 3-day Fitness Boxing Trial Version, available now on the Nintendo eShop on Nintendo Switch. 

Learn more about Fitness Boxing on Nintendo Switch! https://goo.gl/hnyz8m

#NintendoSwitch #FitnessBoxing
